Package oogasalad.editor.view

Class ConditionsSectionBuilder

java.lang.Object
oogasalad.editor.view.ConditionsSectionBuilder
public class ConditionsSectionBuilder extends Object
Builds the UI section for managing Conditions associated with an Event. Handles condition groups, adding/removing conditions by type (String) and index, and provides UI for parameter editing. Uses separate functional interfaces for handlers and a separate class for display items.
Author:
Tatum McKinnis
